  <section style="background-color: #FFFFFF; border-top: 1px solid #E5E0D8; border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E0D8; padding: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px) 24px;">
    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <span style="display: inline-block; font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #3D5A3E; margin-bottom: 12px;">Alderley Edge buyer FAQ</span>
      <h2 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 30px); font-weight: 700; color: #1C1C1E; line-height: 1.25; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">What do buyers ask about living in Alderley Edge?</h2>
      <p style="font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #444444; margin: 0 0 24px 0;">Alderley Edge property searches consistently raise the same due diligence questions - from whether the village justifies its Golden Triangle premium to how school admissions work when no secondary school sits within the SK9 7 boundary.</p>
