      <h2 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 30px); font-weight: 700; color: #1C1C1E; line-height: 1.25; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">Where else should Alderley Edge buyers consider in Cheshire?</h2>
      <p style="font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #444444; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Buyers shortlisting Alderley Edge typically compare it against Wilmslow for commute speed, Knutsford for market-town character, and Prestbury for rural seclusion. Each guide below covers prices, schools, and transport for a direct comparison.</p>
